
---

# .gitignore

Create a file named **.gitignore** and paste this:

```gitignore
# Python cache files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Virtual Environment
venv/
env/
.venv/

# Environment variables
.env

# IDE settings
.vscode/
.idea/

# Operating system files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Jupyter Notebook files
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Build files
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
